      <iTunesMetadata xmlns="http://music.apple.com/lyric-ttml-internal">
        <translations>
          <translation type="subtitle" xml:lang="zh-Hans">
            <text for="L1">保持朋友关系 这是我们唯一能做的</text>
            <text for="L2">保持朋友关系 是时候说再见了</text>
            <text for="L3">保持朋友关系 这是我们唯一能做的</text>
            <text for="L4">保持朋友关系……</text>
            <text for="L5">脑中浮现 昨天一大早</text>
            <text for="L6">好像是在收拾打破的玻璃碎片的情景</text>
            <text for="L7">这到底是什么情况？ 被割伤的手指滴下了血滴</text>
            <text for="L9">我们真的干了</text>
            <text for="L10">这种蠢事吗？</text>
            <text for="L11">我很清楚 在心底深处</text>
            <text for="L12">最难过的选择才是最佳答案</text>
            <text for="L13">不断抗拒的是自我保护</text>
            <text for="L14">和自我矛盾的无限循环</text>
            <text for="L15">我什么时候</text>
            <text for="L16">才说的出口呢？</text>
            <text for="L17">慢慢腐朽的这个世界</text>
            <text for="L18">不断挣扎的我只剩一条活路</text>
            <text for="L19">将你褪色的微笑 刻划在我心中</text>
            <text for="L20">然后拔掉忍耐的栓子</text>
            <text for="L21">喊叫到声嘶力竭</text>
            <text for="L22">反响 残响 空虚地响着</text>
            <text for="L23">就算把锁给解开</text>
            <text for="L24">也什么都不会留下</text>
            <text for="L25">两人相遇的偶然</text>
            <text for="L26">暗转 断线 无尽虚幻</text>
            <text for="L27">“反正就是这样啦” 如此低语</text>
            <text for="L28">流在毫无生气的脸庞上的 是谁的眼泪</text>
            <text for="L29">这是我们唯一能做的</text>
            <text for="L30">保持朋友关系 是时候说再见了</text>
            <text for="L31">保持朋友关系 这是我们唯一能做的</text>
            <text for="L32">保持朋友关系 保持朋友关系 保持朋友关系……</text>
            <text for="L33">我才发现 在昨晚风雨停息过后</text>
            <text for="L34">就算把掉在地上的花瓣给捡起来</text>
            <text for="L35">它再也无法绽放</text>
            <text for="L36">掌心这微小的死亡</text>
            <text for="L37">让我们两人的时间</text>
            <text for="L38">就此停滞</text>
            <text for="L39">我想起了 我们初次相遇的季节</text>
            <text for="L40">你那温柔笑着的脸庞</text>
            <text for="L41">就把现在变成过去</text>
            <text for="L42">两人遍体鳞伤</text>
            <text for="L43">我们的内心已满是</text>
            <text for="L44">荆棘般的尖刺</text>
            <text for="L45">面对沉重苦闷的这段感情</text>
            <text for="L46">令人悲伤的是我这不曾变过的心</text>
            <text for="L47">明明是如此深爱 没办法轻易分开</text>
            <text for="L48">但我不说出口不行</text>
            <text for="L49">下在心里的倾盆大雨</text>
            <text for="L50">呆然 竦然 让视线都模糊</text>
            <text for="L51">虽说早已做好觉悟 那份痛楚</text>
            <text for="L52">仍贯穿了我的身体</text>
            <text for="L53">连结两人的羁绊</text>
            <text for="L54">剪断 解开 消失在日常生活中</text>
            <text for="L55">再见了曾深爱的人 到此为止了</text>
            <text for="L56">别再回头就向前走吧</text>
            <text for="L57">一次就好 一次就好</text>
            <text for="L58">愿望可以实现的话</text>
            <text for="L59">不管要转世几次</text>
            <text for="L60">我都会去找寻那时候的你</text>
            <text for="L61">喊叫到声嘶力竭</text>
            <text for="L62">反响 残响 空虚地响着</text>
            <text for="L63">就算把锁给解开</text>
            <text for="L64">也什么都不会留下</text>
            <text for="L65">连结两人的羁绊</text>
            <text for="L66">剪断 解开 消失在日常生活中</text>
            <text for="L67">再见了曾深爱的人 到此为止了</text>
            <text for="L68">别再回头就向前走吧</text>
            <text for="L69">就此划下句点了</text>
            <text for="L70">保持朋友关系 是时候说再见了</text>
            <text for="L71">保持朋友关系 这是我们唯一能做的</text>
            <text for="L72">保持朋友关系 是时候说再见了</text>
            <text for="L73">保持朋友关系</text>
            <text for="L74">保持朋友关系 这是我们唯一能做的</text>
            <text for="L75">保持朋友关系</text>
            <text for="L76">保持朋友关系 是时候说再见了</text>
            <text for="L77">保持朋友关系</text>
            <text for="L78">保持朋友关系 这是我们唯一能做的</text>
            <text for="L79">我们本该 早该如此</text>
            <text for="L80">保持朋友关系 是时候说再见了</text>
            <text for="L81">我们本该 做普通朋友</text>
            <text for="L82">保持朋友关系</text>
          </translation>
          <translation type="subtitle" xml:lang="en">
            <text for="L5">It came to mind in the early morning yesterday</text>
            <text for="L6">As if I gathered broken pieces of glass</text>
            <text for="L7">What the heck is this?</text>
            <text for="L8">A drop from a cut on my finger</text>
            <text for="L9">Is this what we</text>
            <text for="L10">Really hoped for?</text>
            <text for="L11">I knew it at the bottom of my heart</text>
            <text for="L12">That the hardest choice would be the best</text>
            <text for="L13">My self-love refuses it</text>
            <text for="L14">And repeats self-contradiction</text>
            <text for="L15">When can I</text>
            <text for="L16">Tell it to you?</text>
            <text for="L17">In this slowly decaying world</text>
            <text for="L18">I&apos;m struggling but it&apos;s the only way</text>
            <text for="L19">Carving your faded smiles</text>
            <text for="L20">I pulled out the plug</text>
            <text for="L21">I screamed with my hoarse voice</text>
            <text for="L22">Rebound and resonance echo in vain</text>
            <text for="L23">Nothing is left behind at the end</text>
            <text for="L24">Of the me that has been unchained</text>
            <text for="L25">The coincidences that we&apos;d piled up</text>
            <text for="L26">Degenerate into the dark and are broken in pieces</text>
            <text for="L27">&quot;No matter what we do, life is just like that.&quot;</text>
            <text for="L28">I mumbled as somebody&apos;s tears flow down the dried cheeks</text>
            <text for="L33">Yesterday a tranquil night made me realize</text>
            <text for="L34">It&apos;d be useless to pick up fallen petals</text>
            <text for="L35">Because it&apos;d never bloom again</text>
            <text for="L36">It&apos;s tiny but already dead on my palms</text>
            <text for="L37">Our time</text>
            <text for="L38">Stopped long ago</text>
            <text for="L39">I remember the season we first met</text>
            <text for="L40">And your graceful smile</text>
            <text for="L41">Bringing up old issues</text>
            <text for="L42">We hurt each other as badly as possible</text>
            <text for="L43">Our hearts are</text>
            <text for="L44">Full of thorns</text>
            <text for="L45">With this continuous dull relationship</text>
            <text for="L46">Grievously I can&apos;t change my mind</text>
            <text for="L47">I still love you, I don&apos;t wanna be apart from you</text>
            <text for="L48">But I have to tell you</text>
            <text for="L49">It&apos;s raining heavily in my mind, I&apos;m stunned,</text>
            <text for="L50">I&apos;m standing dead, my vision is blurry</text>
            <text for="L51">Despite my determination,</text>
            <text for="L52">The pain is still penetrating</text>
            <text for="L53">The bond between us had come apart</text>
            <text for="L54">And is dying away in everyday</text>
            <text for="L55">Goodbye, my sweetheart, it&apos;s over</text>
            <text for="L56">We had to leave without turning back</text>
            <text for="L57">Just once, just once</text>
            <text for="L58">If I could have my wish to come true</text>
            <text for="L59">I&apos;d be born again and again</text>
            <text for="L60">And go see you on those days</text>
            <text for="L61">I screamed with my hoarse voice</text>
            <text for="L62">Rebound and resonance echo in vain</text>
            <text for="L63">Nothing is left behind at the end</text>
            <text for="L64">Of the me that has been unchained</text>
            <text for="L65">The bond between us had come apart</text>
            <text for="L66">And is dying away in everyday</text>
            <text for="L67">Goodbye, my sweetheart, it&apos;s over</text>
            <text for="L68">We had to leave without turning back</text>
            <text for="L69">It&apos;s all over</text>
          </translation>
        </translations>
